(58, 2, '2014-01-08 10:20:57', '2014-01-08 10:20:57', 'We are looking for an experienced graphic designer who produces creative of the highest level for a fantastic London agency. Someone who is passionate about creating and designing identities, digital experiences including UI, apps and websites, film and motion projects for leading global brands. This agency is currently involved in some stunning, exciting projects and this means they need a creative of the highest calibre otherwise there''s no point.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Creative designer who has a breadth of understanding across all digital platforms.</li>\r\n	<li>A strong portfolio that demonstrates branding and website design</li>\r\n	<li>Be able to create a visual language from identity &amp; guidelines, through to collateral and website</li>\r\n	<li>Knows how to build a brand from scratch across a digital space.</li>\r\n	<li>Has experience of working with global brands and specialist start-ups alike.</li>\r\n	<li>Wants to produce leading edge design day in day out.</li>\r\n	<li>Understands how to design responsive websites.</li>\r\n	<li>Expert in Adobe Creative Suite.</li>\r\n	<li>Work will be innovative and inspirational.</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate, motivated and extremely creative</li>\r\n	<li>Strong typography, layout &amp; technical skills</li>\r\n	<li>Organised, good communication skills</li>\r\n	<li>Interest in film and motion direction is a plus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary is £23k - £28k depending upon experience.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV and portfolio.\r\n\r\nYou must have a valid UK work visa or European passport to apply for this role.', 'Creative Designer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'creative-designer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:28:10', '2014-01-08 10:28:10', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=58', 3, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(59, 2, '2014-01-08 10:25:05', '2014-01-08 10:25:05', 'A fantastic independent London based creative agency is seeking a great Account Manager/Senior Account Manager to join their team and work primarily with a home electronics client. This established integrated agency work with exciting lifestyle brands and have delivered beautifully crafted, award-winning campaigns for some world class names. It is a great opportunity to work with a growing agency that has real ambition to work with the best people and deliver work that makes their clients famous.\r\n\r\nAs an Account Manager/Senior Account Manager you need to be at the top of your game and looking to push your career forward with the desire to climb the career ladder in the future.\r\n\r\nThe ideal candidate will be…\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A highly talented AM/SAM with 3-5 years of agency experience and an understanding of the home electronics industry</li>\r\n	<li>Someone who is passionate to work on a high profile account</li>\r\n	<li>A proactive and entrepreneurial self-starter who can work well in a team and individually</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to lead digital, retail promotions, events, as well as strategic brand-led communications</li>\r\n	<li>A strong leader with solid project management skills, able to set clear expectations</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to mentor, motivate and develop Account Executive and Account Manager’s careers</li>\r\n	<li>Someone who has a full comprehension of the agency process and financial management</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to run the daily output of the agency and help grow their offering</li>\r\n	<li>Strategically minded, ambitious, patient, level headed and highly collaborative</li>\r\n	<li>Good eye for creative work and strong attention to detail</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated experience, including strong digital, ATL &amp; BTL credentials</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou must have a visa to work in the UK or a European passport to apply for this role.\r\n\r\nSalary £25 - £32k dependent on experience.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV.', 'Account Manager / Senior Account Manager', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'account-manager', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:25:48', '2014-01-08 10:25:48', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=59', 2, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(63, 1, '2013-12-30 19:11:31', '2013-12-30 19:11:31', '<p dir="ltr" id="docs-internal-guid-5ee12b13-76ff-21a5-1229-0214c2a7c49f">I’m a digital recruitment consultant.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">After graduating with a degree in Fashion and Marketing I began my career at Marks &amp; Spencer where I gained valuable business and commercial management experience. I then moved to Sydney and freelanced with various advertising and branding agencies where I worked as part of a team of talented creatives and managers.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr"><!--more-->I am a team player with strong communication skills, and the confidence and ability to work with candidates and clients across across all levels of business. I’m excited to be working in the digital creative industry. I love to review creative portfolios and help candidates achieve their career goals.</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr">I smile a lot too.</p>\r\nYou can see my full CV <a title="Melissa Phillips on LinkedIn" href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/melissa-phillips/3a/848/940" target="_blank">here</a>.', 'Melissa Phillips', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'melissa-phillips', '', '', '2014-02-21 10:18:56', '2014-02-21 10:18:56', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=people&#038;p=63', 2, 'people', '', 0),
