(164, 2, '2014-01-08 10:21:26', '2014-01-08 10:21:26', 'Are you a talented and aspiring creative team with core digital experience looking for your next challenge? If so, one of London’s top advertising agencies need you. This role will be working with the Executive Creative Director and Creative Director’s, working on a variety of key accounts such as FMCG, Lifestyle, Technology, Telecoms and Retail. Plenty of scope for great experience and the  opportunity to build an amazing portfolio of digital work.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1-2 years core digital experience in an agency environment</li>\r\n	<li>Must be a creative team comprising of copywriter and art director</li>\r\n	<li>Strong digital portfolio bursting with creative ideas and demonstrates good strategic thinking</li>\r\n	<li>Proven track record of delivering ideas across different digital platforms (advertising, web, mobile, social)</li>\r\n	<li>Big idea generators with capability to develop multi platform campaigns</li>\r\n	<li>Confidence to concept, create and present new ideas to the team</li>\r\n	<li>Full understanding of social media and how to use this as a platform</li>\r\n	<li>Good cultural fit for the agency, demonstrating open, agile, curious and affable characteristics</li>\r\n	<li>Problem solvers, prepared to help the team find creative solutions through delivery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary - £25 - 35k dependent on experience.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.\r\n\r\nYou must have full UK work visa or European passport to apply for this role.', 'Digital Creative Team (Copywriter & Art Director)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'digital-creative-team-copywriter-art-director', '', '', '2014-01-09 11:39:55', '2014-01-09 11:39:55', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=164', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(165, 2, '2014-01-08 10:24:43', '2014-01-08 10:24:43', 'An award winning advertising agency is looking for a digital design lead to join their design team. The ultimate opportunity to be part of a collective of high-end digital experts who work across an extraordinary roster of clients. You must have lots of creative flair, deliver exquisite digital thinking and visual design execution, and be an intelligent, ambitious, passionate and innovative creative and designer.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Highly talented creative designer with 8+ years of creative agency experience</li>\r\n	<li>Must have an entrepreneurial mindset and a relentless passion for beautiful crafted design, change and innovation</li>\r\n	<li>Bring lots of inspiration to the team by encouraging big ideas and innovative design approaches</li>\r\n	<li>Be able to work across a diverse number of projects, solve problems and keep within tight deadlines</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to lead, mentor and inspire work of others, including freelancers and 3rd party design studios</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with creative, technology, user experience and strategy to create beautiful experiences</li>\r\n	<li>Have worked across a breadth of high impact and multiple platforms - desktop, tablet mobile and IPTV</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent communicator within the team and when liaising with client groups</li>\r\n	<li>Assist in hiring digital design resource when needed</li>\r\n	<li>Exceptional portfolio showing creative thinking and beautifully strong digital design across multiple channels for desktop, tablet, mobile and IPTV</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nMust have a visa to work in the UK or European passport.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV and link to your portfolio.', 'Digital Design Lead', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'digital-design-lead', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:33:38', '2014-01-08 10:33:38', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=165', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(166, 2, '2014-01-08 10:31:09', '2014-01-08 10:31:09', 'We are looking to recruit a <b>brilliant Digital Producer</b> to work at a fantastic six year old creative agency that specialises in helping start ups and established brands grow through innovation and smart creative ideas.\r\n\r\nThis agency''s key to success is innovation, smart strategy, product development and creative marketing. They have helped many brands develop and launch content strategies across social and digital and product development projects run from new mobile apps to food products. Collaboration is their ethos and runs through everything they do and their approach.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>At least 2 years agency experience</li>\r\n	<li>Strong experience of running digital builds, wireframes and creating user journeys.</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent project management is essential, strong track record in delivering projects on-time and on-budget</li>\r\n	<li>Be confident in managing clients and external agencies at both a local and global level.</li>\r\n	<li>Happy to get stuck in to every task and be a strong team player</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary £25k negotiable on experience.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV.\r\n\r\nYou must have a UK work visa or European passport to apply for this role.', 'Digital Producer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'digital-producer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:31:09', '2014-01-08 10:31:09', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=166', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(167, 2, '2014-01-08 10:33:03', '2014-01-08 10:33:03', '<b></b>A fantastic Head of Design position has come up at a top 10 London integrated advertising agency. They work with a range of clients across automotive, FMCG, finance, beauty, travel and alcohol among others, producing award-winning campaigns. You could be looking for that up step up to design director or currently at this level and have an amazing integrated portfolio.\r\n\r\nThey are looking for an inspirational, ambitious design director who can lead, mentor and grow the integrated design team. The candidate must be able to understand how a brand works, take a step back to evaluate and assess the right direction for every brand going forward. Used to working across multiple clients and delivering visual design across integrated campaigns that include, TV, Print, Websites, Social, Applications and other media. You would be working closely with the Executive Creative Director, Technical Director and lead the design team across multiple accounts.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strong experience in advertising, design or digital agency</li>\r\n	<li>A fantastic portfolio bursting with integrated campaigns across various platforms</li>\r\n	<li>Highly passionate about design and obsessive attention to detail</li>\r\n	<li>Experience of working with specialists such as photographers and illustrators</li>\r\n	<li>Lots of pitching and presenting to clients and the team externally and internally</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent understanding of key design principles such as layout and typography</li>\r\n	<li>Solid knowledge of User Experience, Interaction Design and Web Design</li>\r\n	<li>Be able to lead, mentor and inspire others within the team and across agency</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to evaluate and assess what each brand needs then direct and oversee</li>\r\n	<li>Good understanding of Adobe Creative Suite and strong technical knowledge</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary: £80k dependent on experience.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.\r\n\r\nMust have a UK work visa or European passport to apply for this role.', 'Head of Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'head-of-design', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:33:13', '2014-01-08 10:33:13', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=167', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(168, 2, '2014-01-08 10:36:00', '2014-01-08 10:36:00', 'A growing and fast paced product and service design studio with an impressive client list are looking for a confident, talented and enthusiastic <b>Interaction Prototyper / Front-End Developer</b> to join their multi-disciplined service design team. Working closely with visual UX designers on every project You’ll take high-level concepts and quickly develop them into functioning, interactive prototypes. With talented in house design, strategy and development you will feel enabled to deliver world class products and services for leading brands.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2+ years experience in a fast-paced working environment turning challenging concepts into solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Have a background in digital and multi-media design and development</li>\r\n	<li>Collaboratively work with creative teams to Design great products and services for their clients</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to develop for and test across a wide range of browsers, platforms and devices</li>\r\n	<li>Work with designers to ensure UX Design concepts are technically implementable</li>\r\n	<li>Work  closely with offsite development teams to ensure usability, flexibility and maintainability</li>\r\n	<li>Good working knowledge of all standard design tools, front end technologies and development languages</li>\r\n	<li>Build prototypes to spec and be creatively involved in the design process, creating solutions for users and clients</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTechnical Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Advanced knowledge of HTML / CSS / XML /JavaScript / jQuery / JSON / AJAX experience</li>\r\n	<li>Worked within server-side templates written in node.js / ASP.Net / PHP</li>\r\n	<li>Performance and debugging tools like Chrome DevTools / Firebug / Fiddler</li>\r\n	<li>Version control systems such as Subversion / Github</li>\r\n	<li>CSS compilers such as LESS / SASS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary £25 - 30k depending on experience.\r\n\r\nApplicants must have a UK working visa or a European passport to be considered for this role.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.', 'Interaction Prototyper / Developer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'interaction-prototyper-developer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:36:00', '2014-01-08 10:36:00', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=168', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(169, 2, '2014-01-08 10:37:37', '2014-01-08 10:37:37', 'A growing and fast paced product and service design studio based in London with an impressive client list. Are looking for a confident, dynamic and strong Lead User Experience Designer to join their design team.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4+ years of UX design experience from agency or client side background</li>\r\n	<li>Strong Conceptual thinker with a pixel perfect eye for interface design, typography and interaction</li>\r\n	<li>Be able to prototype ideas and love making them come to life</li>\r\n	<li>Create sketches, wireframes and prototypes to tell compelling stories</li>\r\n	<li>Strong researcher and understand customer personas and user journeys</li>\r\n	<li>Articulate creative ideas, present and inspire the team and clients</li>\r\n	<li>Lead projects and mentor less experienced team members</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent knowledge of Adobe design tools and front end technologies</li>\r\n	<li>Comfortable talking about digital brand experiences and focus groups</li>\r\n	<li>Experience of designing for cross platform products and service design</li>\r\n	<li>Share design knowledge and best practices in the industry</li>\r\n	<li>Must be intelligent, eager and passionate about producing high end design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPlease send an up to date CV and link to your portfolio. Only successful applicants will be contacted.', 'Lead UX Designer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lead-ux-designer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:38:08', '2014-01-08 10:38:08', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=169', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(171, 2, '2014-01-08 10:40:02', '2014-01-08 10:40:02', 'An award winning global advertising agency is looking for a mid-weight digital designer to join their design team. A great opportunity to be part of a collective of high-end digital experts who work across an extraordinary roster of clients. You must have lots of creative flair and deliver exquisite digital thinking and design execution, and be an intelligent, ambitious, passionate and innovative designer.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Highly talented digital designer with 4+ years of creative agency experience</li>\r\n	<li>Have an incredible eye for detail across typography, design, motion and 3D</li>\r\n	<li>Bring lots of inspiration to the team through innovative design approaches</li>\r\n	<li>Confident in creating design concepts, from quick visual mock ups to polished designs</li>\r\n	<li>Be able to work across a diverse number of projects and keep within tight deadlines</li>\r\n	<li>Can lead, mentor and provide support to junior members of the design team</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to collaborate with UX, Technology, Creative and Production team</li>\r\n	<li>Worked across a breadth of multiple platforms - desktop, tablet and mobile</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent communicator within the team and when liaising with production partners</li>\r\n	<li>Passionate about making things from within the agency and self-initiated projects</li>\r\n	<li>Exceptional portfolio showing creative thinking and beautifully strong craft skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPlease send an up to date CV and link to your portfolio.\r\n\r\nMust have a visa to work in the UK or European passport. Only successful applicants will be contacted.', 'Mid-weight Digital Designer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mid-weight-digital-designer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:40:07', '2014-01-08 10:40:07', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=171', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(172, 2, '2014-01-08 10:41:37', '2014-01-08 10:41:37', 'We are looking for a Business Developer for an independent, fast growing and award-winning agency. They design digital products and services that drive innovation for brands, agencies and new technology start-ups. They have taken the best of the agency model, the best of start-up culture and a few secret ingredients of their own to build something entirely new. A three year old agency that specialise in not only production but also design and strategy, using product development methodology to deliver innovative, creative and technical projects to create outstanding digital experiences.\r\n\r\nThe Business Developer is responsible for sustaining the revenue growth, developing new business opportunities for digital products and services within the mobile and web space. This person must be a super connector with an outstanding knowledge of the current UK and global market dynamics. An outstanding network of major contacts is essential to enable the agency to bring the sharp skills and unique services they offer to a new audience.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Strong experience in advertising, design and/or digital industry</li>\r\n	<li>Good understanding of product and services industry competitors and how to grow the business to compete</li>\r\n	<li>4+ years of solid experience in business development in the digital products and services industry</li>\r\n	<li>Work with the founders to budget for new business efforts and opportunities across desired industries</li>\r\n	<li>Good understanding of creative and development project life cycles to confidently convey agency services and offering</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent Account Management skills in particular experience in mediation, negotiation and presentation</li>\r\n	<li>Achieve revenue and profitability targets throughout the bid and proposal process</li>\r\n	<li>Formulate and execute plans to build long-term partnerships with current and new clients</li>\r\n	<li>Strong communicator and negotiator of contracts and service-level agreements</li>\r\n	<li>Must also have experience working with cross functional teams such as planning, design and technology</li>\r\n	<li>Team player with strong influencing skills, extremely organised, analytical and dynamic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSalary: £60k + commission structure.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.', 'Business Developer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'business-developer', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:41:37', '2014-01-08 10:41:37', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=172', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(173, 2, '2014-01-08 10:43:51', '2014-01-08 10:43:51', 'A fantastic independent London based creative agency is seeking a great Senior Account Manager to join their team and work with two fashion clients. This established integrated agency work with big names in the fashion and lifestyle industry and have delivered beautifully crafted, award-winning campaigns for some world class brands.\r\n\r\nIt is a fantastic opportunity to work with a growing agency that has real ambition to work with the best people and deliver work that makes their clients famous.\r\n\r\nAs a Senior Account Manager you need to be at the top of your game and looking to push your career forward with the desire to become an Account Director in the future.\r\n\r\nThe ideal candidate will be…\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A highly talented SAM with 5+ years of agency experience and an understanding of the fashion sector</li>\r\n	<li>Someone who is passionate to work on a creative, high potential and high profile account</li>\r\n	<li>A proactive and entrepreneurial self-starter who can work well in a team and individually</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to lead digital and retail promotions, as well as more strategic brand-led communications</li>\r\n	<li>A strong leader with good management skills, able to set clear expectations</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to mentor, motivate and develop Account Executive and Account Manager’s careers</li>\r\n	<li>Someone who has a full comprehension of the agency process and financial management</li>\r\n	<li>Patient, level headed and highly collaborative</li>\r\n	<li>Strategically minded, ambitious, with the will to succeed</li>\r\n	<li>Good eye for creative work and strong attention to detail</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated experience, including strong digital, ATL &amp; BTL credentials</li>\r\n	<li>A visa to work in the UK or a European passport</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV.', 'Senior Account Manager', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-account-manager', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:43:51', '2014-01-08 10:43:51', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=173', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(174, 2, '2014-01-08 10:45:17', '2014-01-08 10:45:17', 'We are looking for an outstanding creative team to join the London office of a fantastic digital agency. They are currently one of the fastest growing digital agencies in Europe and working with fantastic diverse brands, and currently a top secret integrated project. Strong board-level relationships with global clients, this place is bursting with opportunity to create exciting innovative work.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Must be passionate and eager creative team with strong digital/creative agency experience</li>\r\n	<li>Able to craft their idea with inspiring art direction and copy that is a pleasure to read</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to take a brief, run with it and come back with a range of routes</li>\r\n	<li>Motivated, highly creative individuals who are keen grow with the agency and open more opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Thrive on working in a challenging environment and be a strong communicator internally and with clients</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent understanding of technology''s capabilities and  knowledge of latest trends and innovations</li>\r\n	<li>An award-winning portfolio with digital advertising, branded content, social media, experiential and retail</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nYou will be working closely with a fantastically experienced creative director and an amazing strategy team. An exciting opportunity to grow at an agency that is going places.\r\n\r\nSalary up to £60k.\r\n\r\nPlease send an up to date CV and link to online portfolio.\r\n\r\nYou must have a valid UK work visa or European passport to apply for this role.\r\n\r\nDue to the number of applications, regrettable we are only able to contact successful candidates.', 'Senior Digital Creative Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-digital-creative-team', '', '', '2014-01-08 10:45:17', '2014-01-08 10:45:17', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=174', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(175, 2, '2014-01-08 10:46:42', '2014-01-08 10:46:42', 'An award winning London creative design agency are looking for a senior digital designer to join their team. Be able to bring energy, enthusiasm and strong design ideas across digital and interactive projects. Working closely with the Digital Design Director to help shape and grow the digital team.\r\n\r\nEssential:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Solid 6+ years of digital design agency experience</li>\r\n	<li>Must be an ambitious, passionate and hardworking designer</li>\r\n	<li>Highly motivated and passionate about producing high quality design</li>\r\n	<li>Exceptional understanding of user interface, interactive and rich media</li>\r\n	<li>Team player who can work under direction but also able to use own initiative</li>\r\n	<li>A conceptual thinker who can communicate and articulate ideas to the design team</li>\r\n	<li>Experience of taking the design from concept, through development and ready for production</li>\r\n	<li>Solid experience of working on a range of projects from desktop, mobile, interactive and live events</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent typography and UI crafting skills with proficient skills in Adobe creative Suite</li>\r\n	<li>Must have an amazing portfolio full of strong creative ideas and through to execution</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPlease send an up-to-date CV and link to your portfolio site. Only successful applicants will be contacted.', 'Senior Digital Designer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-digital-designer', '', '', '2014-01-08 13:22:14', '2014-01-08 13:22:14', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=175', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(176, 2, '2014-01-08 10:48:25', '2014-01-08 10:48:25', 'An innovative, fast growing and dynamic start up company, who are backed by the best online and social businesses out there. Have an exciting opportunity for a UI/UX designer to help shape and mould their offering, taking ownership of a key part of their business.\r\n\r\nEssential Requirements:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Highly talented UX/UI Designer with a BA Hons Design degree</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent portfolio showing effective and responsive visual UI and UX design</li>\r\n	<li>Must be passionate, smart, ambitious, collaborative designer</li>\r\n	<li>An understanding of how to create user experiences and user flows</li>\r\n	<li>Interested or have experience of usability and running user testing workshops</li>\r\n	<li>Take a project through from initial concepts through to design and execution</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate well with marketing, customer support, technology and product teams</li>\r\n	<li>Strong visual eye for detail across typography, design and layout</li>\r\n	<li>Can talk through design ideas and present well to the team</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent skills with Adobe software, specifically Photoshop and Illustrator</li>\r\n	<li>A bonus if you have HTML, CSS and Javascript, to help prototype ideas</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nPlease send an up-to-date CV and link to your portfolio.\r\n\r\nOnly successful applicants will be contacted.', 'UX/UI Designer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'uxui-designer', '', '', '2014-02-23 11:39:39', '2014-02-23 11:39:39', '', 0, 'http://hellomavis.local/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=176', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
